column5: Is the Tee Pee Motel closed? I called them today, and got a fast busy signal. I did some quick googling and saw they had a fire last fall. Let me know what the story is. I apologize if there is another thread on this. I didn't see one.
Call the Chamber of Commerce. 1-800- FallsMn
Let's just go camping. Are the Martin boys coming?
What happened to the walleye wrangler?
TeePee had a fire and is closed. Hasnt been torn down yet either
